<p rend="chapter">Dāsaka kaṇḍa</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="292"><hi rend="paranum">292</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Antojāto <pb ed="M" n="0.0176" /> dhanakkīto, dāsabyopagato sayaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Dāsākaramarānīto-ccevaṃ te catudhā siyuṃ.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="293"><hi rend="paranum">293</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Pubbuṭṭhā pacchānipātī, dinnassa ādāyīpi ca;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Sukatakammakaro ca, kittivaṇṇaharopi ca.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="294"><hi rend="paranum">294</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Dāsā 0.0177 pañceva corayya-sakhāñātyattasādisā;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Tathā viññūhi viññeyyā, mittadārā ca bandhavā.</p>
